OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1775408752
OL,3,COne of world's tiniest antelopes born
OL,4,Cat Chester Zoo
OL,6,FDotty and her mum at Chester Zoo
OL,8,FOne of the world's smallest baby
OL,9,Fantelopes has taken her first steps at
OL,10,FChester Zoo - standing barely taller
OL,11,Fthan a tin of baked beans.
OL,13,FThe tiny Kirk's dik-dik fawn, named
OL,14,FDotty by zoo staff, was born on
OL,15,FFebruary 17 weighing just a few
OL,16,Fhundred grams. When fully grown,
OL,17,Fshe'll reach just 40cm tall - making
OL,18,Fher one of the smallest antelopes on
OL,19,Fthe planet.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/4
