PN,39804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1775408752
OL,3,COne of world's tiniest antelopes born
OL,4,Cat Chester Zoo
OL,6,FThey use their elongated, flexible
OL,7,Fnoses to pluck leaves directly from
OL,8,Fbranches - a unique feature found only
OL,9,Fin dik-diks - and mark their territory
OL,10,Fusing scent glands beneath their eyes
OL,11,Fand between their toes.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/4
